Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:49.87,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's when she looked down
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:55.31,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and realize she was wearing purple socks with the burgundy dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.86,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Purple and burgundy, darlings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:04.61,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The same color family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:13.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was a terrifying story.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.31,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm terrified she'll try to tell it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.88,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anyone else have a spooky story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:21.98,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:25.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I'm warning you, you might as well hug your friend now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:28.56,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's how scary it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.58,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:37.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's time I told you about the legend of Gaia Everfree.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:47.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Many years ago my great grandparents came to this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.98,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Seeing its beauty, they decided that it would be the perfect place for a camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:20:00.22,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But once they started building, strange things started to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:06.21,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,One pitch-black night, when the wind was howling,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:09.11,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,a tree branch crashed through the roof of their cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:11.14,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They screamed and ran outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,only to see the giant creature rising from the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.71,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,She got wild hair, like the roots of a tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Her mouth had jagged rock teeth and her eyes were pools of black tar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But her aura shimmered like diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:28.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Anywhere she went, she left a trail of gemdust in her wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.46,0:20:32.38,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Trembling, my great grandparents asked who she was and what she wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:38.01,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In a deep and hollow voice she told them that her name was Gaia Everfree –
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,an ancient spirit who held domain over the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and that my great grandparent were trespassing on her land.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They begged her to let them stay and build their camp
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:49.46,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,to share this wonderful place with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.08,0:20:52.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gaia Everfree finally agreed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:55.48,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but warned them that they would not be able to keep it forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:21:00.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Some day she will return and reclaim the forest as her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:05.73,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So if you see a trail of gemdust, you'll know that it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.58,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gaia Everfree!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:14.01,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Sorry, didn't mean to scare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.22,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then why did you come out of the bushes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:21.01,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I... took the scenic route, because the forest is beautiful at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:24.29,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But no one else should without a guide, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Alright, everybody, time to head to you tents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:30.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, Gloriosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:33.41,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you have extra toothbrushes? I forgot mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:37.11,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sure do! I'll get one for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.11,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm scared of the dark! Do you have flashlights?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.98,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Of course! I got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.93,0:21:48.28,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:52.51,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Spike. I guess that story got to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:54.79,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why? It can't be real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.26,0:21:56.48,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:00.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gaia Everfree some creature that got booted from Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.20,0:22:01.53,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and ended up in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:03.58,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's what happened with the Sirens.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.61,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Eh. Sounded more like something that Timber was making up just to scare us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.95,0:22:10.51,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At least I hope it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:14.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Last thing I want is to have camp ruined by some power-crazed magical creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.17,0:22:16.41,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, hear-hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.59,0:22:18.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We had to deal with more than our fair share of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:22.97,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At the Fall Formal, a musical showcase, the Friendship Ga–
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.51,0:22:27.11,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean, you know, everything turned out alright, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:32.08,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mmm. I'm kinda tired. I'm in a turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:35.77,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe lay off bringing up what happened at the Friendship Games?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.19,0:22:38.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I think she's still pretty sensitive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:42.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our lips are sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.27,0:22:52.37,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:56.63,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:02.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm always here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:02.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:05.11,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who's there? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.68,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Sorry, Sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:14.08,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Uh, Twilight, I think something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.78,0:23:20.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Is it time to get up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:25.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twilight, we really have to talk about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:27.22,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, we don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.22,0:23:43.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, I know you don't want to,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:46.42,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I really think we need to figure out what's going on with your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.99,0:23:48.58,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you could learn to control it–
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:51.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's just it! I'll never be able to control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:57.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:01.78,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We didn't see anything, so we don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.56,0:24:06.41,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:09.41,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.50,0:24:12.68,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We were stuck in a middle of the lake with no wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:15.08,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,then all of a sudden BAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.27,0:24:18.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The wind picked up and we were pushed right into the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.05,0:24:22.29,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You don't think it was the spirit, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.86,0:24:24.72,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.40,0:24:29.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Spirit, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.45,0:24:33.18,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Great and Powerful Trixie commands it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.53,0:24:34.57,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.83,0:24:43.91,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, man! All our hard work! Ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.07,0:24:46.07,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At least the fishes are really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.29,0:24:48.19,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let's salvage what we can out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.30,0:24:49.78,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can still fix this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:53.78,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We have to try! Camp Everfree needs our runway!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.06,0:24:54.78,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.98,0:24:57.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dock, yes, that's what I meant.
